title: Tig Notaro Returns
description:
Tig Notaro feels gay about being Conan O’Brien’s friend.

 

Tig sits down with Conan once again to discuss which of her kids she thinks is going into comedy, favorite jokes and pranks, and her inability to identify celebrities. Plus, Conan and his team issue an inaugural broadcast from their brand new podcast space.

 

Got a question for Conan? Call our voicemail: (323) 451-2821.

 

For Conan videos, tour dates and more visit TeamCoco.com.
author: conaf@teamcoco.com (Team Coco & Earwolf)
